xxl.core.predicates

Class CountingPredicate<P>

  • java.lang.Object
    • xxl.core.predicates.DecoratorPredicate<P>
      • xxl.core.predicates.CountingPredicate<P>
  • Type Parameters:
    P - the type of the predicate's parameters.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Predicate<P>, Decorator<Predicate<? super P>>

    public class CountingPredicate<P>
extends DecoratorPredicate<P>
    A DecoratorPredicate that provides additional information about calls, hits, and misses to its inner predicate.
